text: Wout-Jan van der Schans (born 12 May 1961) is a Dutch equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ede, Netherlands
